import React from 'react';
import {chevronBack} from 'ionicons/icons'
import {
  IonContent,
  IonHeader,
  IonList,
  IonPage,
  IonRefresher,
  IonRefresherContent,
  IonTitle,
  IonToolbar,
  useIonViewWillEnter,
  IonButtons,
  IonBackButton,
  IonCard,
  IonCardTitle
} from '@ionic/react';
import './Indexes.css';

const Indexes: React.FC = () => {

  

  return (
    <IonPage id="Indexes">
      <IonHeader>
        <IonToolbar>
          <IonButtons  slot="start">
          <IonBackButton defaultHref="/home" icon={chevronBack} />
        </IonButtons>
          <IonTitle>Indexes</IonTitle>
        </IonToolbar>
      </IonHeader>
      <IonContent fullscreen>
      <IonCard>
        <IonCardTitle>Alphabetic Index</IonCardTitle>
      </IonCard>

      <IonCard>
        <IonCardTitle>Numeric Index</IonCardTitle>
      </IonCard>
    
      </IonContent>
    </IonPage>
  );
};

export default Indexes;
